 @startuml School Management System

actor Student
participant "View Educational Information" as ViewInfo
participant "Submit Assessments" as SubmitAssessments
participant "Complete Tasks" as CompleteTasks
participant "Update Educational Information" as UpdateInfo

Student -> ViewInfo: View Educational Information
ViewInfo --> Student: Display Educational Information

Student -> SubmitAssessments: Submit Assessments
SubmitAssessments -> UpdateInfo: Update Educational Information

Student -> CompleteTasks: Complete Tasks
CompleteTasks -> UpdateInfo: Update Educational Information

@enduml
